== OpenSUSE
## Login information
# user: root
# pass: testtest
- SSH enabled on boot with root login
## System details
- emulated Intel 6300ESB WatchDog
- no graphic card
- serial console configured for system and grub
- hostname configured according to VM_NAME from fast-vm
- [!!] system installd by hand with 'Server' profile (minimal package selection)
- system would be running for the first time after installation
## Drive layout
- 6 GB drive
  - 8MB - BIOS boot device
  - LVM name (os15vg)
    - 256MB swap_lv
    - 5GB root_lv
    - rest is free space on VG os15vg
